    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, transfer the <strong>smoky butter</strong> to a bowl, reserving the pan</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Add your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until the tomatoes start to blister – these are your <strong>blistered tomatoes</strong></p>",
