    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced ciabatta</strong> to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through – these are your <strong>toasts</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and<strong> </strong>your<strong> roasted garlic paste </strong>in a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic yoghurt</strong></p>",
