    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>cucumber[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut your<strong> avocado[s] </strong>in half lengthways, around the stone</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh </strong>and slice into quarter</p>",
