    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> and <strong>sliced cucumber </strong>in a bowl with the <strong>remaining cider vinegar </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>cucumber salad</strong></p>",
