    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dollop the <strong>roasted garlic yoghurt </strong>onto a plate and top with a <strong>poached egg </strong>and spoon over the <strong>smoky butter</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>blistered tomatoes</strong>, <strong>sliced avocado</strong>, <strong>cucumber salad </strong>and the <strong>toasts </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
